{"tid":1220340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢wargame要全民black bloc 杯弓蛇影 草木皆兵","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:00:51.000Z","uid":98603,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0f5df3cf1a676996bdb399bdd6fae9864655a5","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Black boc係保護自己同隊友<br />\n琴晚發夢<br />\n見到所有人今日開始 所有人出街都全黑 黑衫黑褲 盡量黑鞋，袋都要黑<br />\n全部買冇logo 明顯特徵既淨色tee同褲，黑色外套<br />\n背囊都盡唔好用有logo<br />\n背囊每面每人一套基本裝備+頭盔<br />\n口罩/豬嘴 眼罩/泳鏡 急救用品，<br />\n如有就加多本毛語錄同習語錄擺頂<br />\n一打開就見到<br />\n其他裝備自行發揮<br />\n（記者朋友已經幫我地助攻）<br />\n俾人查就講普通話<br />\n杯弓蛇影 草木皆兵 <br />\n一個人引人注意 當全世界都咁做<br />\n你就係一個群體<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"04e8be2da9ff8d510183cb411e2165d42296ffc1","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"def4f75ba15d6e2b2b6e02996ee1849d217df611","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a68aa5721ff4c8e9ea4feca398aacbd3ccc2e059","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d45ae2c80fde405388f0fe299d4d62be7e04490","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78536fa651c4a71e784dfbf549e26e32854d950d","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"305ae065ee28d127aa7d5dfcf0145fe55803425b","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36c0e777502bc5f18dbf8fc09cc9097a5356425c","tid":1220340,"uid":98603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72c1c6c38bf9d6a8de145f1192c5b04f528011e2","tid":122034